name: Glassmorphism Icon
description:
Experience even more flexibility with Glassmorphism Icon Packs. Change the color, stroke and effects of the icon or just its individual elements.
 
PRODUCT FEATURES
All shapes are vector-based
Smooth and rounded corners
Easy to change the style (Support Figma's Variants)
Easy to change colors
 
FILE INCLUDES
Figma file (library of components and support variants)
SVG files
